This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image segmentation using convolutional neural networks. It may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories as these fields are closely related to computer vision. Additionally, it may belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category as it deals with medical image analysis. Finally, it may belong to the neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-category as it uses neural networks for segmentation.
